            . I have known him some time; he was looked upon as a very honest young man.</p>
               <p>For Hughes.</p>
               <p>Wil. Mould. I have known Hughes betwixt five and six years; he lodged and boarded along with me. He never wronged me; he bore a good character.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17700530-47-person437">
