               <p>All three <rs id="t17700530-47-verdict264" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17700530-47-verdict264" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>. <rs id="t17700530-47-punish265" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17700530-47-punish265" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
