                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17700530-47-defend422 t17700530-47-punish266"></join>
               They received sentence immediately, this being Friday, to be executed on the Monday following, and their bodies to be dissected and anatomized.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>There was an indictment against them for a robbery on the highway.</p>
               <p>The blunderbuss was the property of the Genoese ambassador, whose house was lately broke, and that with other things stole, &amp;c.</p>
